<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Refund Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #DF9E7C;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #c87c5a;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .email-body h1 {
            color: #DF9E7C;
        }
        .email-body p, .email-body h1 {
            text-align: left;
        }
        .email-body ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-body ul li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .button-link {
            display: block;
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 10px auto;
            background-color: #DF9E7C;
            color: #000000; /* Set text color to black */
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .button-link:hover {
            background-color: #c87c5a;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #DF9E7C;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h2>Fatima's Therapy Services</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <h1>Refund Confirmation</h1>
            <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
            <p>Your refund for booking number <strong>{{bookingId}}</strong>, booked for <strong>{{eventDate}}</strong> at <strong>{{eventTime}}</strong> has been processed. It may take up to 10 days to show in your account.</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Payment Amount:</strong> {{paymentAmount}} pkr</li>
                <li><strong>Payment Status:</strong> {{paymentStatus}}</li>
                <li><strong>Paid on:</strong> {{paymentCompleted}}</li>
                <li><strong>Transaction Reference Number:</strong> {{transactionReferenceNumber}}</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:{{adminEmail}}">{{adminEmail}}</a>.</p>
            <p>Thank you for your understanding and cooperation.</p>
            <p>Sincerely,</p>
            <p>Fatima's Therapy Services</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} Fatima's Therapy Services. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
